cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with image clustering using deep autoencoder for feature representation learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also focuses on learning discriminative features for clustering, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG and cs.AI). The paper also deals with multimedia (cs.MM) as it involves image clustering. Finally, the paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with grouping similar images in a cluster.
